<div id="t">LISA DAVIDSON CERAMICS</div>
<div id="st">Hand Made Vases and Bowls</div>

<h1>Home</h1>
<p>Welcome.</p>

<p>I am a ceramic artist working in stoneware clays.</p>

<p>I hand build ceramic vases, bowls and creature-style vessels, embellished with a variety of textures and geometric lines, using a combination of Art Deco, Egyptian and Retro styles.</p>

<p>All my ceramic art is created through hand-coiling and press moulding to give true individuality to each piece, down to the finishes, vibrant glazes and metallic lustres.</p>

<p>I have been commissioned for a wide range of galleries in the UK and abroad and I have exhibited at Whitleys, <a href="http://www.newdesigners.com/">The New Designers</a>, The Midsummer Art Fair at Teddington and The Thomas Kettle Gallery in Covent Garden. I am also a member of <a href="http://teddingtonartists.co.uk/">The Teddington Artists</a> and The Craft Movement.</p><div id="f">&copy; Lisa Davidson Ceramics 2016</div>
